'''Oxonmoot 2015''', the 42nd annual [[Oxonmoot]] hosted by [[The Tolkien Society]], took place [[10 September|10]]-[[13 September]] at St Antony's College, [[University of Oxford|Oxford]]. As with [[Oxonmoot 2014]], Oxonmoot 2015 was an extra day long.
